tags:
---
Matthias: Hi, {$playerName}! 
Matthias: I'm glad you came. 
Matthias: I'm just about to take this little row boat out to a nearby cove. 
Matthias: If it's not too much trouble, would you like to come with me?
    -> Yeah. Lead the way!
        Matthias: That's great! 
        Matthias: Don't worry, I'll do all the rowing.
        <<jump chapter3_OmenCity_Harbour_Matthias2>>
    -> Player: No thanks.
        Matthias: Oh...
        Matthias: Don't worry, I understand. 
        Matthias: Sorry to have bothered you, {$playerName}.
