title: chapter3_OmenCity_OmenArrowrootWildsGate
tags:
---
Guard: Halt!
Guard: Amulet, please.
<<if $AmuletRank == "Bronze" and $OmenDate == 0>>
    Guard: Apologies, Adventurer. 
    Guard: It is getting late. 
    Guard: The Wilds will be too dangerous. 
    Guard: Come back in the morning and we will let you through.
<<endif>>
<<if $AmuletRank != "Bronze">>
    Guard: You're not a high enough rank to pass through on foot. 
    Guard: I'd suggest battling the Guild Master here if you want a Bronze amulet.
<<endif>>
<<if $AmuletRank == "Bronze" and $OmenDate == 1>>
    Guard: Good luck out there, Adventurer!
<<endif>>
===

title: chapter3_OmenCity_Inn
tags:
---
Innkeeper: Hi, Adventurer! 
Innkeeper: Tonight we're hosting a special, romantic dinner for the Candlelight Festival.
Innkeeper: Would you like me to make you a reservation?
    -> Player: Yes.
        <<if $Invitation_Accepted == 1>>
            Innkeeper: Excellent! 
            Innkeeper: Come and speak to me again once you've done all your adventuring for the day and I'll get your table ready.
        <<endif>>
        <<if $Invitation_Accepted == 0>>
            Innkeeper: Ah, it seems you don't have anyone to dine with yet. 
            Innkeeper: My apologies, it's tables for two only.
        <<endif>>
    -> Player: Not yet.
        Innkeeper: You'd better hurry and pluck up the courage to ask someone before we fill up!
===

